About this item

  • DESIGNED FOR KIDS: Premium quality headphones reimagined for kids, with distance learning, travel, and streaming online content in mind. These headphones feature a 3.5mm wired audio connection, so your child will always have a stable audio connection.
  • BUILT-IN MICROPHONE & SAFE SOUND: The wire has a built-in microphone for video and phone calls. And with Belkin Signature Sound with audio tuned specifically for kids, this headphone set has an 85dB volume limiter to protect your little one's ears.
  • COMFORTABLE DESIGN: SoundForm Mini is cleverly crafted for a wide range of boys and girls, with an over-the-ear design and comfortable, kid-sized cushions. This headset also has a built-in micro-USB port for charging (micro-USB to USB-A cable included).
  • KID FRIENDLY CONTROLS: Kids won't need any help setting up or using their wired headphones, as simple one-button touch mic control on the cable turns sound on and off for kids to enjoy their favorite music and more.
  • OOPS PROOF MATERIALS & FUN STICKERS: These kids wired headphones are durability tested to withstand 3,000 uses, surviving spills and accidents for up to 2 years. And kids can get creative and customize their headset with the included stickers!

    Product Description

    Keep your kids ears comfortable and protected with premium wired on-ear headphones designed just for them. Intuitive controls on the 3.5mm audio cable are perfect even for young children, whether theyre doing schoolwork online or watching videos in the back seat. A volume cap of 85dB protects their hearing, and durability testing assures these headphones are safe from damage from spills and accidents for up to 2 years. Theyre designed to work with popular distance learning devices and apps. Connect these headphones to any compatible iOS or Android device and enjoy all your favorite sounds.

    Belkin is an established accessories market leader creating high-quality, innovative tech solutions for 40 years.

    Specifications:
    Cup Width: 2.7in/69.5mm
    Headband Width: 6.7in/171mm
    Compatibility: Any device with 3.5mm audio output jack
    2-year limited warranty

    SoundForm Mini Wired On-Ear Headphones for Kids

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

    Learn more how customers reviews work on Amazon

    Customers say

    Customers find these headphones perfect for kids, with decent sound quality and good value for money. They fit well and are easy to connect via Bluetooth, though some report connectivity issues. The durability and functionality receive mixed feedback - while some find them durable, others report them breaking within weeks, and while they work well for travel, some mention they stopped working.

    Amazon Customer
    5 out of 5 stars
    Great for school, or home, fits small heads, pressure causes discomfort after prolonged wear
    Belkin is an audio brand we trust and ordered these for our eight year old son. The sound limiting is legit and works. My son has been using these for the past year and now uses them at school( with the included cord) on his classroom Chromebooks. The headphones have always fit his tiny head just fine but he does complain of "hot ear" and discomfort from the constant pressure of the headphones cups pressing on his ears. Usually thats after wearing them for an hour or more but honestly the cups could be slightly larger, or replaceable, and could fit around the ear better. My son prefers using them in wired mode simply because it's less hassle when connecting between devices and there's less chance of technical or connectivity issues. Overall these have proven to be dependable, high quality headphones that have seen a ton of use over the past year and will hopefully see us through this school year. I predict my son will out grow the headphones before the headphones stop working.

    About this Item

    • DESIGNED FOR KIDS: Premium quality headphones reimagined for kids, with distance learning, travel, and streaming online content in mind. These headphones feature a 3.5mm wired audio connection, so your child will always have a stable audio connection.
    • BUILT-IN MICROPHONE & SAFE SOUND: The wire has a built-in microphone for video and phone calls. And with Belkin Signature Sound with audio tuned specifically for kids, this headphone set has an 85dB volume limiter to protect your little one's ears.
    • COMFORTABLE DESIGN: SoundForm Mini is cleverly crafted for a wide range of boys and girls, with an over-the-ear design and comfortable, kid-sized cushions. This headset also has a built-in micro-USB port for charging (micro-USB to USB-A cable included).
    • KID FRIENDLY CONTROLS: Kids won't need any help setting up or using their wired headphones, as simple one-button touch mic control on the cable turns sound on and off for kids to enjoy their favorite music and more.
    • OOPS PROOF MATERIALS & FUN STICKERS: These kids wired headphones are durability tested to withstand 3,000 uses, surviving spills and accidents for up to 2 years. And kids can get creative and customize their headset with the included stickers!

    Product Description

    Keep your kids ears comfortable and protected with premium wired on-ear headphones designed just for them. Intuitive controls on the 3.5mm audio cable are perfect even for young children, whether theyre doing schoolwork online or watching videos in the back seat. A volume cap of 85dB protects their hearing, and durability testing assures these headphones are safe from damage from spills and accidents for up to 2 years. Theyre designed to work with popular distance learning devices and apps. Connect these headphones to any compatible iOS or Android device and enjoy all your favorite sounds. Belkin is an established accessories market leader creating high-quality, innovative tech solutions for 40 years. Specifications: Cup Width: 2.7in/69.5mm Headband Width: 6.7in/171mm Compatibility: Any device with 3.5mm audio output jack 2-year limited warranty Package Includes: SoundForm Mini Wired On-Ear Headphones for Kids 3.5mm audio cable Fun stickers Based on sales of SoundForm kids products made from February 2021 through March 2024
